---
title: Pan-Fried Garlic Herb Gnocchi with Brussels Sprouts & Sun-Dried Tomatoes
description: Pan-frying just about anything builds up extra flavor—and these gnocchi are proof. You’ll start with pillowy potato gnocchi, which you’ll cook in butter until brown and crisp. They get tossed with sun-dried tomatoes and Brussels sprouts. A swirl of garlic herb butter and dusting of Parmesan take the rich and umami flavors to the next level. Pour yourself a glass of wine, you’re ready to toast to a restaurant-worthy dinner in just 20 minutes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pan-fried-garlic-herb-gnocchi-b98a3cc7.jpg
